E_D("replace into `news_data` values('3397','大忌:千万别把床头朝向西方极乐世界!','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 14px; line-height: 27.4286px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ZEuh5NGC76JnR7T16bcw7Dua15cshYPySMwBsezwp5m0pN99nRWicVTnnA4iaJKTrZicia3CEySsxU3yIONEcAlpng/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" width=\"auto\"/><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">风水学以为，床之位置，影响人体健康、运势、子嗣及夫妇关系。床位摆放若触犯了风水禁忌，则可能让你是非不断，身体受损。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">1、床头忌朝西。古人以西方为「极乐世界」，乃死后向往之所。即以现代科学观点言之，亦属欠妥。盖日落西方，地球自转由东而西，头向西而眠，久之，易致血液上冲耳。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2、床底忌紧连地面。床下至宜通风、清洁，以防止感染阴湿之气，致碍健康。床下勿置杂物，尤忌铁器、玻璃。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">3、床忌冲门。床之为物，止供卧眠，最宜宁静、安全，而门属长动之物，时有开阖，倘使直冲（或横冲）门户，自然弊端横生，故非所宜。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">4、床忌接近窗户。床头不宜太接近窗户。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">5、床忌背门。人卧于床第视门，务须一目了然，否则易受干扰、惊吓，影响情绪健康。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; font-size: 18.018px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.028px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; 